== Events == * {{ill|Chōhō|ja|長保}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} [[999]] [[December 11]]) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michinaga|ja|藤原道長}}’s daughter, {{ill|Akiko|ja|藤原彰子}}, was received into court.{{要出典|date=2021-03}} * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1863]] [[December 11]]) – The {{ill|Satsuma Domain|ja|薩摩藩}} paid 100,000 dollars to an English envoy, resolving the {{ill|Namamugi Incident|ja|生麦事件}}.{{要出典|date=2021-03}}
== Births == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} [[1561]] [[December 7]]) – {{ill|Yoshikawa Hiroie|ja|吉川広家}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Suō Province|ja|周防国}}’s {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国領}} (died [[1625]]). * {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} [[1275]] [[November 19]]) – {{ill|Musō Soseki|ja|夢窓疎石}}, a monk of the {{ill|Rinzai Zen|ja|臨済宗}} (died [[1351]]). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1847]] [[December 8]]) – {{ill|Nakajima Chōmin|ja|中江兆民}}, a thinker (died [[1901]]).
