* {{ill|Chōhō|ja|長保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[999]] [[December 11]]) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michinaga|ja|藤原道長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’s daughter, {{ill|Akiko|ja|藤原彰子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, was received into court.{{要出典|date=2021-03}}
* {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1863]] [[December 11]]) – The {{ill|Satsuma Domain|ja|薩摩藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} paid 100,000 dollars to an English envoy, resolving the {{ill|Namamugi Incident|ja|生麦事件|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.{{要出典|date=2021-03}}

== Births ==
* {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1561]] [[December 7]]) – {{ill|Yoshikawa Hiroie|ja|吉川広家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Suō Province|ja|周防国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’s {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国領|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1625]]).
* {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1275]] [[November 19]]) – {{ill|Musō Soseki|ja|夢窓疎石|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a monk of the {{ill|Rinzai Zen|ja|臨済宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1351]]).
* {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1847]] [[December 8]]) – {{ill|Nakajima Chōmin|ja|中江兆民|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a thinker (died [[1901]]).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Daireki|ja|大暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ([[776]]) – {{ill|Xinping Princess|ja|新平公主|zh|新平公主 (唐朝)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, daughter of {{ill|Emperor Xuanzong|ja|玄宗|zh|玄宗 (唐)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Commemorations ==
* 朔旦冬至 (if this day coincides with the {{ill|Winter Solstice|ja|冬至|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}})

