{{Lunisolar November}}
'''November 1''' is the 1st day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=draft}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Chōhō|ja|長保|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[999]] [[December 11]]) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michinaga|ja|藤原道長|qq=draft}}’s daughter, {{ill|Akiko|ja|藤原彰子|qq=draft}}, was received into court.{{要出典|date=2021-03}}
* {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1863]] [[December 11]]) – The {{ill|Satsuma Domain|ja|薩摩藩|qq=draft}} paid 100,000 dollars to an English envoy, resolving the {{ill|Namamugi Incident|ja|生麦事件|qq=draft}}.{{要出典|date=2021-03}}

== Births ==
* {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1561]] [[December 7]]) – {{ill|Yoshikawa Hiroie|ja|吉川広家|qq=draft}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Suō Province|ja|周防国|qq=draft}}’s {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国領|qq=draft}} (died [[1625]]).
* {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1275]] [[November 19]]) – {{ill|Musō Soseki|ja|夢窓疎石|qq=draft}}, a monk of the {{ill|Rinzai Zen|ja|臨済宗|qq=draft}} (died [[1351]]).
* {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1847]] [[December 8]]) – {{ill|Nakajima Chōmin|ja|中江兆民|qq=draft}}, a thinker (died [[1901]]).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Daireki|ja|大暦|qq=draft}} 10th year ([[776]]) – {{ill|Xinping Princess|ja|新平公主|zh|新平公主 (唐朝)|qq=draft}}, daughter of {{ill|Emperor Xuanzong|ja|玄宗|zh|玄宗 (唐)|qq=draft}}.
== Commemorations ==
* 朔旦冬至 (if this day coincides with the {{ill|Winter Solstice|ja|冬至|qq=draft}})

