== Births == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eiroku|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1561]] [[December 7]]) – {{ill|Yoshikawa Hiroie|ja|吉川広家|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yoshikawa Hiroie|qq=}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Suō Province|ja|周防国|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suō Province|qq=}}’s {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国領|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwakuni Domain|qq=}} (died [[1625]]). * {{ill|Kenji|ja|建治|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenji|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1275]] [[November 19]]) – {{ill|Musō Soseki|ja|夢窓疎石|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Musō Soseki|qq=}}, a monk of the {{ill|Rinzai Zen|ja|臨済宗|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rinzai Zen|qq=}} (died [[1351]]). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōka|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1847]] [[December 8]]) – {{ill|Nakajima Chōmin|ja|中江兆民|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakajima Chōmin|qq=}}, a thinker (died [[1901]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Daireki|ja|大暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daireki|qq=}} 10th year ([[776]]) – {{ill|Xinping Princess|ja|新平公主|zh|新平公主 (唐朝)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinping Princess|qq=}}, daughter of {{ill|Emperor Xuanzong|ja|玄宗|zh|玄宗 (唐)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Xuanzong|qq=}}. == Commemorations == * 朔旦冬至 (if this day coincides with the {{ill|Winter Solstice|ja|冬至|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Winter Solstice|qq=}})
