== Births == * [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 4th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1561|1561]] [[December 7]]) – [[:en:Kikkawa Hiroie|Yoshikawa Hiroie]], the first lord of the [[:en:Suō Province|Suō Province]]’s {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国領|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwakuni Domain|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 岩国藩}} (died [[:en:1625|1625]]). * [[:en:Kenji (era)|Kenji]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1275|1275]] [[November 19]]) – [[:en:Musō Soseki|Musō Soseki]], a monk of the [[:en:Rinzai school|Rinzai Zen]] (died [[:en:1351|1351]]). * [[:en:Kōka|Kōka]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1847|1847]] [[December 8]]) – [[:en:Nakae Chōmin|Nakajima Chōmin]], a thinker (died [[1901]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Daireki|ja|大暦|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daireki|qq=}} 10th year ([[776]]) – {{ill|Xinping Princess|ja|新平公主|zh|新平公主 (唐朝)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinping Princess|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, daughter of {{ill|Emperor Xuanzong|ja|玄宗|zh|玄宗 (唐)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Xuanzong|qq=}}. == Commemorations == * 朔旦冬至 (if this day coincides with the [[:en:Winter solstice|Winter Solstice]])
