{{Lunisolar November}}
'''November 1''' is the 1st day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|WD=Q96759844|1=taian}}{{efn|ja|大安|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|1=taian|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1306255}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Chōhō (era)|en|Chōhō (era)|WD=Q1324844|lt=Chōhō|1=Chōhō (era)}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|999|en|999|WD=Q277307|lt=999|1=999}} {{ill|December 11|en|December 11|WD=Q2363|lt=December 11|1=December 11}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michinaga|en|Fujiwara no Michinaga|WD=Q433133|lt=Fujiwara no Michinaga|1=Fujiwara no Michinaga}}’s daughter, {{ill|Empress Shōshi|en|Empress Shōshi|WD=Q901949|lt=Akiko|1=Empress Shōshi}}, was received into court.{{Citation needed|date=2021-03}}
* {{ill|Bunkyū|en|Bunkyū|WD=Q730266|lt=Bunkyū|1=Bunkyū}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1863|en|1863|WD=Q7701|lt=1863|1=1863}} {{ill|December 11|en|December 11|WD=Q2363|lt=December 11|1=December 11}}) – The {{ill|Satsuma Domain|en|Satsuma Domain|WD=Q676187|lt=Satsuma Domain|1=Satsuma Domain}} paid 100,000 dollars to an English envoy, resolving the {{ill|Namamugi Incident|en|Namamugi Incident|WD=Q546075|lt=Namamugi Incident|1=Namamugi Incident}}.{{Citation needed|date=2021-03}}

== Births ==
* {{ill|Eiroku|en|Eiroku|WD=Q1143341|lt=Eiroku|1=Eiroku}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1561|en|1561|WD=Q6618|lt=1561|1=1561}} {{ill|December 7|en|December 7|WD=Q2299|lt=December 7|1=December 7}}) – {{ill|Kikkawa Hiroie|en|Kikkawa Hiroie|WD=Q1049766|lt=Yoshikawa Hiroie|1=Kikkawa Hiroie}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Suō Province|en|Suō Province|WD=Q1053037|lt=Suō Province|1=Suō Province}}’s {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国領|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwakuni Domain|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 岩国藩|1=Iwakuni Domain|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q839263}} (died {{ill|1625|en|1625|WD=Q6826|lt=1625|1=1625}}).
* {{ill|Kenji (era)|en|Kenji (era)|WD=Q1327993|lt=Kenji|1=Kenji (era)}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1275|en|1275|WD=Q5529|lt=1275|1=1275}} {{ill|November 19|en|November 19|WD=Q3026|lt=November 19|1=November 19}}) – {{ill|Musō Soseki|en|Musō Soseki|WD=Q384703|lt=Musō Soseki|1=Musō Soseki}}, a monk of the {{ill|Rinzai school|en|Rinzai school|WD=Q639625|lt=Rinzai Zen|1=Rinzai school}} (died {{ill|1351|en|1351|WD=Q6104|lt=1351|1=1351}}).
* {{ill|Kōka|en|Kōka|WD=Q1325317|lt=Kōka|1=Kōka}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1847|en|1847|WD=Q7644|lt=1847|1=1847}} {{ill|December 8|en|December 8|WD=Q2301|lt=December 8|1=December 8}}) – {{ill|Nakae Chōmin|en|Nakae Chōmin|WD=Q2972146|lt=Nakajima Chōmin|1=Nakae Chōmin}}, a thinker (died {{ill|1901|en|1901|WD=Q2035|lt=1901|1=1901}}).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Daireki|ja|大暦|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daireki|1=Dali|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10935673}} 10th year ({{ill|776|en|776|WD=Q30690|lt=776|1=776}}) – {{ill|Xinping Princess|ja|新平公主|zh|新平公主 (唐朝)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinping Princess|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, daughter of {{ill|Emperor Xuanzong|ja|玄宗|zh|玄宗 (唐)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Xuanzong|1=Emperor Xuanzong|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11572271}}.
